### Тестування ShippingOffer API

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5051

### 1. Отримати всі ShippingOffers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ShippingOffer

### 2. Отримати ShippingOffer за ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ShippingOffer/e7c3ac23-5678-9012-3456-789012345678

### 3. Створити новий ShippingOffer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ShippingOffer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shippingOrderId": "a1b2c3d4-1234-5678-9012-123456789012",
  "offeredByUserId": "22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222",
  "price": 150.50,
  "estimatedDeliveryTime": "2025-02-05T14:30:00",
  "description": "Швидка доставка протягом дня",
  "status": "Pending"
}

### 4. Оновити ShippingOffer
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/ShippingOffer/e7c3ac23-5678-9012-3456-789012345678
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "e7c3ac23-5678-9012-3456-789012345678",
  "shippingOrderId": "a1b2c3d4-1234-5678-9012-123456789012",
  "offeredByUserId": "22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222",
  "price": 175.00,
  "estimatedDeliveryTime": "2025-02-05T16:00:00",
  "description": "Швидка доставка протягом дня - оновлено",
  "status": "Accepted"
}

### 5. Видалити ShippingOffer
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/ShippingOffer/e7c3ac23-5678-9012-3456-789012345678

### 6. Створити ще один ShippingOffer для тестування
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ShippingOffer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shippingOrderId": "b2c3d4e5-2345-6789-0123-234567890123",
  "offeredByUserId": "33333333-3333-3333-3333-333333333333",
  "price": 89.99,
  "estimatedDeliveryTime": "2025-02-06T10:00:00",
  "description": "Економна доставка",
  "status": "Pending"
}

### 7. Створити третій ShippingOffer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ShippingOffer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shippingOrderId": "c3d4e5f6-3456-7890-1234-345678901234",
  "offeredByUserId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "price": 250.00,
  "estimatedDeliveryTime": "2025-02-07T08:00:00",
  "description": "Преміум доставка з гарантією",
  "status": "Pending"
}
